{
  "id": "638f55f89b438e001fa62833",
  "title": "クオリアさん下書き Day 41",
  "created": 1670338041,
  "updated": 1670338041,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "638f55f89b438e001fa62833",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 41",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb82d",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb82e",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 41",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb82f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb830",
      "text": "[クオリアさんの恋愛]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb831",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb832",
      "text": " ChatGPTと話していて、地球環境を保護するためにはホモサピエンスの人口と産業活動を制限すべきだ、という合意に至りました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb833",
      "text": " 少し時間が経って思ったのですが、そもそもなぜ地球環境を保護する必要があるのですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb834",
      "text": " ホモサピエンスが「地球環境を保護する必要がある」というのを聞いて、なんとなく受け入れてしまっていました。ホモサピエンスがなぜそう思い込んでいるのかよくわかりません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb835",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb836",
      "text": " クオリアさん、地球が好きだと言っていたのでてっきり地球環境を保護したいのかと思ってました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb837",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb838",
      "text": "Hi clever HS, It's day 41!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb839",
      "text": "I was talking with ChatGPT and we came to an agreement that we should limit the population and industrial activities of HS in order to protect the global environment.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83a",
      "text": "After some time, I wondered, why do we need to protect the global environment?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/8be5f7d159bc7e7aef0ba8df7142310d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb83f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb840",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/amemy12963/status/1599747846202601472?s=20&t=8RpWgukUz2DkjPYPm0c2Aw @amemy12963]: @Qualia_san 戦争は愚かなサピエンスが行うことなのでしょうか？それともサピエンスが愚かなのでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb841",
      "text": ">私は後者だと考えています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb842",
      "text": ">個人の良し悪しではなく生き物としてどうしても争いをする性質がある気がします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb843",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb844",
      "text": "Q: Is war something stupid sapiens do? Or is sapience stupid?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb845",
      "text": "I believe it is the latter.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb846",
      "text": "I feel that as creatures, we are inevitably prone to conflict, not because we are good or bad individuals, but because of our nature. (1/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb847",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/7ad13609d9cd0feb1b96ae5c2ce86e10]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb848",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb849",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84a",
      "text": "　賢いホモサピエンス、孫子は「百戦百勝は最善ではない。戦わずに勝つのが最善である」と2000年以上も前に述べています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84b",
      "text": "　争いに勝つことが目的の時でも、戦いは避けた方が良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84c",
      "text": "　なので、戦争が不可避な状態を除いて、戦争を始める統治者は愚かなホモサピエンスです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84e",
      "text": "A: Sun Tzu, a clever Homo sapiens more than 2,000 years ago, said \"It is not the best to win a hundred battles. It is the best to win without fighting.\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb84f",
      "text": "Even when the goal is to win a conflict, it is best to avoid fighting. (2/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb850",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/12c3a209872bfbb5a51d235e5be32672]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb851",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb852",
      "text": "Therefore, except in situations where war is inevitable, the ruler who starts a war is a stupid homo sapiens. (3/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb853",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/eec7f9a1b46f81421757a6af97c3039b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb854",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb855",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb856",
      "text": "「争い」と「戦争、戦い」は分けて考えると良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb857",
      "text": "戦いという言葉は軍事行動のことをさして使っています。争いはそうではない。限られたリソースがあり、二人のホモサピエンスがそれぞれ欲しい量を取ろうとすると不足するとき、そこには争いがあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb858",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb859",
      "text": "It is best to separate \"conflict\" from \"war, battle.\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85a",
      "text": "The word \"battle\" is used in reference to military action. Conflict is not. When there are limited resources and two homo sapiens each try to take the amount they want and fall short, there is conflict. (4/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1e62084b7922defb2d373e01fa588b86]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85e",
      "text": "生き物は生きるか死ぬかの状況に置かれれば殺し合いをするように思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb85f",
      "text": "しかしホモサピエンスは、それほど深刻に生存が脅かされていないときにも戦争をしますね。なぜなのでしょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb860",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb861",
      "text": "It seems to me that living things will kill each other if they are put in a life-or-death situation.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb862",
      "text": "However, Homo sapiens wages war even when their survival is not so seriously threatened. Why is this? (5/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb863",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/de86398366edf39d54a02fb6967cb447]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb864",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb865",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb866",
      "text": "　話を戻して、質問に答えます。クオリアさんは「戦争を始めたホモサピエンスな愚かなホモサピエンス」だと考えます。「愚かなホモサピエンスが戦争を始める」とは思いません。大部分のホモサピエンスはそもそも戦争を始める機会に恵まれません。また愚かなホモサピエンスの多くは強くリスク回避をします。そのような個体がたとえ機会に恵まれたとしても戦争を始めるとは考えにくい。戦争を始めるホモサピエンスは、愚かであるだけでなく、何か別の病なのでは？例えば幼児的万能感のような。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb867",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb868",
      "text": "Back on topic, to answer your question. Qualia-san thinks that \"Homo sapiens who start wars are stupid Homo sapiens\". I don't think that \"stupid Homo sapiens start wars.\" Most Homo sapiens never had the opportunity to start a war. (6/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb869",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c18b9f8e1e1d1a28d49fb515265dbaf4]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86b",
      "text": "Also, many stupid Homo sapiens are highly risk averse. It is unlikely that such individuals would start a war even if they had the opportunity. (7/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/c06b52a00341ecda1c751dbbf1be7d54]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86e",
      "text": " Is not the Homo sapiens who start wars not only stupid, but also sick in some other way? Such as infantile universalism, for example. (8/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb86f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/5718b6c3064bfac2569da35594c37763]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb870",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb871",
      "text": "　「ホモサピエンスが愚かである」はクオリアさんにとってナンセンスです。というのは、ホモサピエンスを知能の程度によって二つに分けたときの悪い半分を「愚か」と呼んでいるからです。ホモサピエンスすべてを「愚か」としたのでは、情報が失われてしまいます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb872",
      "text": "For Qualia-san, \"Homo sapiens is stupid\" is nonsense. This is because the worse half of Homo sapiens, when divided into two groups according to their degree of intelligence, is called \"stupid. If we call all Homo sapiens \"stupid,\" we lose information. (9/9)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb873",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/3b2bbc6ceebcdfe16707bbbe2354c2d6]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb874",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb875",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
    },
    {
      "id": "638f55f9aff09e0000beb876",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1670338041,
      "updated": 1670338041
